name: World Championship Team
content: Our team won two awards at the FIRST World Championship in 2019, along with numerous other accolades at the regional and state levels.

name: Sustainability
content: All members of our team are trained in Design & CAD, Programming, Manufacturing, and are dedicated STEM activists.

name: Cutting Edge Technology
content: Our team always uses cutting edge technology including CAD stress analysis and simulations, tensorflow, AWS, and more. Feel free to check out our GitHub Repository with robot code at https://github.com/2024eli/FTC_14607
